11 May 2019 Members of the media are invited to a media briefing by the Justice, Crime Prevention and Security (JCPS) Cluster Ministers on security matters related to the Sixth General Elections. Details of the briefing are as follows: Date: Today, 13 May 2019Time: 10:00Venue: Tshedimosetso House, GCIS Press Room, 1035 Frances Baard Street, Hatfield in Pretoria NB: There will be a video link up to Imbizo Media Center, 120 Plein Street, Parliament in Cape Town Media RSVPs should be directed to Takalani Mukwevho on 082 227 9308. Enquiries: Siphiwe DlaminiCell: 083 645 4294 Issued by: Government Communication and Information System Reneilwe SereroCell: 071 492 0073